{"title":"2026 Bespoked UK: Drust Cycles Pinion Cargo Bikes Showcase – Room on the Broom and Klunkargo Safari – John Watson","link":"https://theradavist.com/2026-bespoked-uk-drust-cycles-cargo-bikes","date":1777271441000,"content":"<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/drust-cycles\" target=\"_blank\">Drust Cycles</a> is perhaps best known for the brand’s mini cargo bikes and crazy designs. This year, at the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/2026-bespoked-uk\" target=\"_blank\">2026 Bespoked UK</a> show, Konstantin Drust may have outdone himself with two <a href=\"https://pinion.eu/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Pinion</a> cargo bikes that push the paradigm…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://www.brooksengland.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks England</a> and <a href=\"https://www.schwalbe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Schwalbe</a> for sponsoring our <a href=\"https://www.bespoked.cc/uk-2026\" target=\"_blank\">2026 Bespoked UK</a> coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p>Surely you’d think Konstantin Drust would have won Best Cargo Bike by now. Right? After the judge Jon from <a href=\"https://www.twotoneams.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">Twotone</a> robbed him of the title last year at the 2025 Bespoked Dresden show, the Berlin-based builder dropped two bangers on the crowd, hoping to win them over. Unfortunately, the lads from Sentient went Berzerker and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2026-bespoked-uk-selects-02#:~:text=Sentient%20Works%20Goes%20Full%20Squish%20(es)\" target=\"_blank\">unveiled their project Sherpa</a>, once again denying him the award for Best Cargo Bike and entry into the exclusive <strong>Best Of</strong> Bespoked club like the bouncer Sven at the infamous Berghain club in Berlin.</p>\n<p>All this is in jest; Konstantin doesn’t build for awards. He builds to make his clients and customers happy. So let’s check out what he offered two clients at this year’s show. One is for the owners of Bespoked, and the other is for the owners of this website…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Room on the Broom Mini Velo Cargo</h3>\n<p>Rosie and Petor’s daughter, Leto, has a storybook she loves called “<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0102qfj\" target=\"_blank\">Room on the Broom</a>” about a benevolent witch who invites a dog, bird, and frog to join her on her broomstick. It’s Leto’s favorite book, and so when Petor was looking for a replacement for the family’s Surly Big Dummy, he contacted Konstantin Drust with a sketch of a broomstick cargo bike.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-23.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-23.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-23.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-23.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-22.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-22.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-22.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-22.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Petor wanted the bike to have a large platform rack on the front, to which he’d affix Leto’s child seat. And a rear rack for carrying groceries or their dog, Moondog. The racks are chromoly and engineered to take heavy loads with beefy hardware and solid wall tubing. Like Drust’s steel chassis bikes, they’re fillet-brazed together.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-20.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-20.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The rear end of the rack can be removed for ease of packing and transport. And the bike is geared thanks to the Pinion gearbox. An idler pulley is used to drop the chain away from the elongated chainstays for stability with the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/review-20-astral-outback-wheelset\" target=\"_blank\">20″ Astral Outback wheels</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-24.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-24.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-24.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Broom-Bike-24.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Who needs Berghain when your posse looks this good? Many thanks to Bennet from <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ballern.cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Ballern</a> and Kata from <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rasch.cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Rasch Cycles</a> for posing with the bike!</em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-Cycles-Cargo-Bikes-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>I got to witness the family’s first bike ride, and I think the photo of them riding is my favorite from the show. The look of joy on Leto’s face is outstanding. Petor <span>told me that Leto asked him, <em>“I like this bike. Can we keep it forever?”</em> as they were </span>on its maiden voyage.</p>\n<p>Konstantin Drust makes dream bikes for people with wild dreams.</p>\n<p>I know because I had him build me one, too…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Klunkargo Safari</h3>\n<p>Petor’s muted Room on the Broom is the yin to the Klunkargo Safari’s yang. One is raw steel with black racks; the other is high-vis and loud.</p>\n<p>After my <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cargo-bike-hunting\" target=\"_blank\">bike camping trip in which I harvested an elk last year</a>, I wanted a more off-road-capable cargo bike for potential future exploits. Taking what I <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/omnium-mini-max-review\" target=\"_blank\">liked about the Omnium Mini Max</a> and what I would improve upon it for off-road riding, Konstantin and I started to work out an idea.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-27.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-27.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-27.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-27.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>I came up with the Klunkargo concept, in which the three-bar cruiser frame would extend through the head tube and serve as the rack support. Wanting less standover, we went with a 27.5″ rear wheel and a compact front triangle, with a klunker-inspired top tube kink for a long travel dropper. The rear end fully detaches to make shipping it back to the USA easier, and also for future flights where I might want to take the bike for touring.</p>\n<p>With a detachable front rack, the whole bike packs into a standard bike box. Which is wild!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-4.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>I sent Konstantin a drawing of what I wanted the powder coat to look like with orange parts on the frame, for on-the-road and hunting visibility, but also to add a bit of funky color to my normally drab palette for bike finishes.</p>\n<p>The front wheel is a <a href=\"https://velocityusa.com/collections/rims/products/blunt-35-rim-20?variant=44490877534287\" target=\"_blank\">20″ Velocity Blunt 35</a>, which I quite enjoyed about the Omnium and the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/monopole-cargo-bike-review\" target=\"_blank\">Monopole</a>, but to make it more capable for off-road use, we increased the fork offset considerably. This aids in steering ultra-heavy loads more easily.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.schwalbe.com/en/Rocket-Ron-11654014.01?srsltid=AfmBOopIaGfSe12qHUhNFV7BaC_2kHvapn21vZ0WRtQVi3ket42x9uXf\" target=\"_blank\">Schwalbe Rocket Ron</a> tire comes in 27.5 and 20″, so it was an obvious choice for this bike. I was really impressed with the brand’s green initiatives after my shop visit last year and have moved to include its products on more of my bikes. If you’re curious about the sustainability programs Schwalbe runs, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/schwalbe-headquarters\" target=\"_blank\">my shop visit is worth the read</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-33.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-33.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-33.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-31.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-31.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-31.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-30.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-30.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-30.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>There’s a bit of a genius hack for the dynamo lighting, which was ideated by Flo of <a href=\"https://fern-bicycles.myshopify.com/en-gb\" target=\"_blank\">Fern Bicycles</a>. The lamp wires plug into grommets in the top tube with an internal cable running between the two. So when I take the rack off and the rear end, the lamps can remain intact. For the front lamp, we went with the <a href=\"https://bumm.de/en/product-detail/iq-x/\" target=\"_blank\">Busch &amp; Müller IQ X</a> lamp. The rear lamp is the stunning Allygn <a href=\"https://fern-bicycles.myshopify.com/en-gb/products/allygn-edelmu\" target=\"_blank\">EdelMü</a>, also designed by Flo. It’s attached with a <a href=\"https://fern-bicycles.myshopify.com/en-gb/products/drust-rear-light-mount\" target=\"_blank\">Drust light mount</a>. Both are powered by the legendary <a href=\"https://nabendynamo.de/en/products/hub-dynamos/for-thru-axles/\" target=\"_blank\">SON 28 front hub</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-35.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-35.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-35.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-35.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-20.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-20.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-20.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://pinion.eu/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Pinion</a>‘s mechanical gearboxes are amazing, and I enjoyed <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/pinion-smart-shift-review\" target=\"_blank\">my time with the Smart.Shift</a>, but I wanted something I wouldn’t have to ever charge, so I chose the C1.12 box with the <a href=\"https://tout-terrain.de/en/tt-shift-r-trigger-for-pinion/\" target=\"_blank\">Tout Terrain mechanical shifter</a>. On my few short rides around the block, I’m in love with this setup. The actuation is crisp, and the lever feel is firm. It feels like each shift is intentional. Konstantin donated his <a href=\"https://www.actofive.com/parts/signature-x-pinion-crankset\" target=\"_blank\">ActoFive Pinion cranks</a> to the build. 175 mm of course!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-11.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-11.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-32.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>One standout detail for me is the routing. The non-drive side is super neat and tidy, and in areas where you’ll be removing the attached components, the cables can slide out of the double open-ended hooks, allowing for zero plastic zip tie waste, too. Wow, this guy is really good. It’s almost as if he makes exceptional cargo bikes!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-28.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-28.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-28.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-28.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-34.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-34.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-34.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-34.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-43.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-43.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-43.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-43.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The stunning gunmetal Velocity Blunt 35 rims were laced into glorious wheels by <a href=\"https://munrowheels.de/\" target=\"_blank\">Germany’s Monro Wheels</a>. The front hub is SON 28, and for the high engagement requirements of the Pinion system, we chose a <a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/products/hubs/trial-ss/pro-5-trials-singlespeed-rear-hub/\" target=\"_blank\">Hope Trials SSP hub</a>. I fell in love with Hope <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/inside-hope-tech-uk\" target=\"_blank\">since visiting the factory last year</a> after the Bespoked Manchester show, and wanted as many Hope parts on the build as possible.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-38.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-38.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-38.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-38.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-37.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-37.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-37.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-37.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-23.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-23.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-23.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-23.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/fre/products/brakes/enduro/evo-tr4/\" target=\"_blank\">Hope Rotors, EVO TR4</a>, handlebars, seat collar, and headset are a testament to British design and manufacturing, and yeah, the silver just pops against the black backdrop. I’ve been loving the EVO TR4 brakes on my Black Cat Swami and am looking forward to using them in this application.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-29.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-29.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-29.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-29.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-39.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-39.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-39.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-39.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-15.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-15.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-15.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-15.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gramm-tourpacking.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Gramm Tourpacking</a> made the two-sided frame bags, which I absolutely love. The bolt-on bag looks so elegantly incorporated into the Klunkargo concept. And Tine even made a little frame bag for the triangle. The Berlin woven work didn’t end there…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-22.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-22.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-22.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-22.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-21.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-21.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-21.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-21.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Berlin’s <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vonjott_juicy.bike.stuff/\" target=\"_blank\">Juicy Bike Stuff</a> wove an absolutely insane looking rack platform from cheetah print orange webbing. This is a detail that, personally, I never would have considered, but now that it’s on the bike, it makes me smile every time I see it. So thank you!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-16.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-16.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-16.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-16.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-40.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-40.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-40.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-40.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Last year, Kata Rasch from <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rasch.cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Rasch Cycles</a> built a run of high-rise stems and offered them for sale. These stems were inspired by the work of <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/huntercycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Rick Hunter</a>. Ze Germans love Rick’s work, BTW – Konstantin bought a set of industrial extension cables from Rick during his moving sale and had me forward them to him in Germany.</p>\n<p>I immediately bought one, wanting to support her work, and figured one day I’d build a bike around that very stem. Which we literally did, sizing the frame’s stack height to the exact rise and extension of the stem. It’s a standout detail on a very ostentatious bike, but it’s one that gives me great joy.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-18.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-18.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-18.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-18.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-19.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-19.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-19.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-19.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Still, in all this ridiculousness, it might be the <a href=\"https://www.pnwcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">PNW silver Loam dropper</a> and <a href=\"https://www.brooksengland.com/en_us/flyer.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks Flyer saddle</a> that received the most comments. The dichotomy is so fun and silly, and yes, that saddle is insanely comfy! Plus, it adds to the whole klunker vibes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-45.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-45.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-45.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-45.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Dream bikes come from dreams, and Konstantin Drust is a dream bike builder. The Klunkargo Safari is wild. It’s fun and silly and yet still a wonderfully sculpted tool for everyday commuting, touring, camping, and other activities. It is the result of my life experiences that made me push equipment and my psyche into uncharted territory and emerge with an idea.</p>\n<p>One that was just silly enough for the cargo bike meister to whip up and unveil at the 2026 Bespoked UK.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-46.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-46.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-46.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Drust-Klunkargo-46.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>I am elated at how this bike turned out and with the human who made it. To all the brands that made it a possibility, thank you!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-301.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-301.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-301.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-301.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-300.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-300.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-300.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/2026-Bespoked-UK-Showcase-300.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>… and to <a href=\"https://rtiiika.com/Custom-Bike-Portraits\" target=\"_blank\">RTiiiKA Bike Portraits</a>, I love the drawing! xo</p>\n<p>If you have a dream bike you’d like Konstantin Drust to build you, <a href=\"https://drustcycles.com/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\">drop him a line</a>.</p>\n<p>Konstantin, you are such a wonderful soul. Thank you.</p>\n<p>Many thanks to <a href=\"https://www.bespoked.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Bespoked</a> for bringing together such a wild and talented group of builders.</p>\n<p><em><strong>We’ve got more on the way from the 2026 Bespoked UK in London!</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Which build was your favorite? We’ve got a lot more on the way, so stay tuned…</strong></em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/CoverageSponsoredby_Schwalbe_Brooks.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/CoverageSponsoredby_Schwalbe_Brooks.png?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/CoverageSponsoredby_Schwalbe_Brooks.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/CoverageSponsoredby_Schwalbe_Brooks.png?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://www.brooksengland.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks England</a> and <a href=\"https://www.schwalbe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Schwalbe</a> for sponsoring our 2026 Bespoked UK coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>All of our 2026 Bespoked UK photos are in <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fo/ub22h6il3xptz4rylnp42/AEloQInROxd7SbFXSmyuPWw?rlkey=l5crjp8imc8scm6ufw7a478ug&amp;st=igwozq3p&amp;dl=0\" target=\"_blank\">The Radavist Dropbox</a> for builders to use.</h3>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2026-bespoked-uk-drust-cycles-cargo-bikes\">2026 Bespoked UK: Drust Cycles Pinion Cargo Bikes Showcase – Room on the Broom and Klunkargo Safari</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"6007a5d25032f1a5a5f3e280798ea0183fbaae4be565746e01833c62d7530620","category":"Cycling"}